#AatmanirbharBharatKaBudget
The budget outlines six pillars to strengthen the vision of Atmanirbharta- health & wellbeing, capital & infrastructure, inclusive development, reinvigorating human capital, innovation, R&D, and minimum government & maximum governance.

#AatmanirbharBharatKaBudget
The budget announces a voluntary vehicle scrapping policy, to phase out old and unfit vehicles. This will help in encouraging fuel-efficient, environment-friendly vehicles, thereby reducing vehicular pollution and oil import bill.

#AatmanirbharBharatKaBudget

#AatmanirbharBharatKaBudget

#AatmanirbharBharatKaBudget

#AatmanirbharBharatKaBudget

#AatmanirbharBharatKaBudget
